WEBVTT

00:11.693 --> 00:13.776
<i>Previously on
The Pillars of the Earth:</i>

00:14.979 --> 00:16.883
<i>Stephen's army
has us surrounded.</i>

00:17.003 --> 00:19.081
We've been besieged for weeks.

00:19.414 --> 00:21.799
I'm Tom Builder.
We'd like to repair your church.

00:21.919 --> 00:24.339
We'll quarry this stone
to build our new cathedral.

00:24.407 --> 00:26.209
<i>When my chisel
hits the rock,</i>

00:26.329 --> 00:28.357
it's a song of what will be.

00:29.580 --> 00:31.392
<i>Kingsbridge gets
the rents, the tolls.</i>

00:31.440 --> 00:32.679
It gets the taxes,
the business.

00:32.689 --> 00:35.383
As of next month,
the market moves to Shiring.

00:36.886 --> 00:37.702
Pray with me.

00:37.727 --> 00:39.068
<i>That boy with red hair,</i>

00:39.188 --> 00:40.514
I want him dead by morning.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.892
He can't be dead.

00:49.240 --> 00:50.644
They've captured the king.

00:51.202 --> 00:53.175
I claim you as my prisoner.

00:53.295 --> 00:55.097
- Your brother's been taken.
- Oh God!

00:55.217 --> 00:58.306
Your king lies in a dungeon
to be hanged tomorrow.

00:58.374 --> 01:00.011
Why shouldn't you hang
with him?

01:00.409 --> 01:03.278
All you have to say is
that you betrayed Bartholomew.

01:04.149 --> 01:05.200
Yes! Yes!

01:05.319 --> 01:06.874
See that he's hanged.

01:10.116 --> 01:20.116
